{"title":"泼汗歌","authors":["李盛鸿","高培银"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼汗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东崂山县拖拉机厂  李盛鸿   高培银"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里厂区十里歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道标语横空贴——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“支援农业机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把大汗往下泼！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼！——火似红旗闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼！——机器唱新歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三中全会激人心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼汗越多越快活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往昔汗水往心里流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憋得咱工人满肚子火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日华主席来撑腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有汗水尽情泼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼出钢，泼出铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼出铁牛走沃野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼出情，泼出爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼出红心献祖国！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，汗不尽哟情难遏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起铁人咱浑身热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹竞赛哟，比干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看谁汗水泼得多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼哟泼，泼哟泼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水汇成沸腾的河——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯起满帆摇起橹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机械化航船“河”上过……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}